</taxonomicName>
: named after Mr. M.D. Gallagher for his contribution to fauna of 
<collectingCountry id="F3454DCD0944B21AEEACF9F622FD4C6D" box="[686,758,1578,1604]" name="Oman" pageId="16" pageNumber="467">Oman</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
